OL,5,GThe death of HM The Queen is an event
OL,6,Gall the major broadcasters have
OL,7,Gprepared for. As the national
OL,8,Gbroadcaster though, the BBC needs to
OL,9,Gput an incredible amount of care and
OL,10,Gattention into getting things right.
OL,12,FAny significant errors of judgement
OL,13,Fcould damage both its pedigree as a
OL,14,Fnews broadcaster and its corporate
OL,15,Freputation.
OL,17,FThe corporation has regularly reviewed
OL,18,Fand where necessary revised its plans
OL,19,Fover the years.
OL,3,CWell-rehearsed procedures invoked for
OL,4,CRoyal news coverage
