OL,5,FThe Queen's death was announced after
OL,6,Falmost six hours of rolling news on BBC
OL,7,FOne.
OL,9,FThe simple fact that Buckingham Palace
OL,10,Fhad issued a statement on the Queen's
OL,11,Fhealth was a sign that there was
OL,12,Fserious concern  even though the words
OL,13,Fof the statement itself did not convey
OL,14,Fthe gravity of the situation.
OL,16,FThe fact a statement was made by the
OL,17,FSpeaker of the House of Commons was
OL,18,Falso a sign of real concern.
OL,3,CWell-rehearsed procedures invoked for
OL,4,CRoyal news coverage
OL,22,                                  G2/10
