PS,c000
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F350A1664752882
OL,5,FThe decision to interrupt Bargain Hunt
OL,6,Fand stay with rolling news through the
OL,7,Fafternoon would not have been taken
OL,8,Flightly.
OL,10,FAt this point, it is worth noting that
OL,11,Fthe procedure for interrupting
OL,12,Fprogrammes appears to have changed.
OL,14,FIt now seems to be the case that a
OL,15,Fprogramme will simply be faded to black
OL,16,Fand that the news presenter will
OL,17,Fwelcome viewers to BBC One.
OL,19,FOf course, in the past Presentation
OL,20,Fwould put up a slide and the announcer
OL,21,Fwould hand to the newsroom.
OL,3,CWell-rehearsed procedures invoked for
OL,4,CRoyal news coverage
