OL,5,FAs the afternoon progressed, it was
OL,6,Fnoticeable that Huw Edwards and many
OL,7,Freporters were wearing black. Clearly
OL,8,Fthe possibility of an announcement was
OL,9,Fon their minds.
OL,11,FHowever, until 5pm, ITV was running as
OL,12,Fnormal. There were no news reports or
OL,13,Fchanges to the schedule although one
OL,14,Fstory dominated the ITV Lunchtime News.
OL,16,FThe announcement of Her Majesty's death
OL,17,Fcame around 6.32pm and was made by Huw
OL,18,FEdwards during the rolling news
OL,19,Fprogramme which had replaced the normal
OL,20,FBBC News at Six.
OL,3,CWell-rehearsed procedures invoked for
OL,4,CRoyal news coverage
