OL,5,FA few moments later, BBC Two joined 
OL,6,Fan abrupt fade to black came during
OL,7,Fathletics coverage.
OL,9,FAgain it is noticeable the caption came
OL,10,Ffrom News  not Presentation  and that
OL,11,FHuw made the out-of-vision announcement
OL,12,Fabout programmes being interrupted.
OL,13,FThis would have been in the planned
OL,14,Fprocedures.
OL,16,FBy Friday morning, some of BBC One's
OL,17,Fnormal programmes had moved to BBC Two.
OL,18,FNaturally care will need to be taken to
OL,19,Fensure nothing inappropriate is
OL,20,Faccidentally shown.
