OL,5,FBBC One will resume some normal
OL,6,Fprogramming from this evening but the
OL,7,Fchannel will have a more subdued
OL,8,Fcharacter during the period leading up
OL,9,Fto the State Funeral. It is reasonable
OL,10,Fto expect anything too lighthearted
OL,11,Fwill be dropped.
OL,13,FPresentation needs to be on guard
OL,14,Fagainst the risk of a misplaced trailer
OL,15,For misjudged transition causing
OL,16,Fdifficulties.
OL,18,FIn days gone by, things would have been
OL,19,Fdifferent.
