OL,5,FFormer announcer Reg Sanders tweeted a
OL,6,Fpicture of the caption placed in the
OL,7,FNoddy machine for the death of the
OL,8,FQueen.
OL,10,FThings are going to be a bit different
OL,11,Fon BBC TV for the next few days. We
OL,12,Frehearsed for this moment so many times
OL,13,Fover the years. This caption is from
OL,14,FThe Noddy camera system.
OL,15,Fpic.twitter.com/3n3qY1ibip
OL,17,FExactly how it may have been used is
OL,18,Fnot clear. Perhaps Reg or another
OL,19,Fformer member of Pres staff can offer
OL,20,Fan insight?
