OL,5,FBut I would imagine that in those days
OL,6,Fa procedure like the following would
OL,7,Fhave been adopted.
OL,9,FBBC One and Two would have been brought
OL,10,Ftogether at an agreed time. In the days
OL,11,Fbefore the internet and 24-hour news it
OL,12,Fwould have been possible to agree an
OL,13,Fembargoed time for an announcement by
OL,14,Fthe BBC, ITN and the main national news
OL,15,Fagency the Press Association.
