OL,5,FIf BBC One were closed down  or if BBC
OL,6,FTwo were completely off the air  there
OL,7,Fwould have been sufficient time to get
OL,8,Fboth networks open. Perhaps a caption
OL,9,Fsaying that a news report would follow
OL,10,Fshortly would have replaced the test
OL,11,Fcard or Ceefax, almost like a normal "z
OL,12,Fminus 2".
OL,14,FAfter the news report  read by the
OL,15,Fnewsreader  Presentation would have
OL,16,Fshown the caption tweeted by Reg and
OL,17,Fplayed somber music. At some point,
OL,18,Ffurther news reports would have been
OL,19,Fbroadcast.
